<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 tā néng bāng nǐ jiě wēi nán tuō lí jiān xiǎn hé dāo jiàn,
 tā hé nǐ yī qǐ dù jiāng hé hé nǐ yī qǐ fān gāo shān,
 zhǔ yǔ nǐ tóng zài, nǐ hái jù shéi. zhēn zhèng zhǎo dào le bì fēng gǎng wān.
 rén xīn bài huài, shì jiè zài biàn qiān, tiān kōng yě bù zài cháng lán,
 zhǔ wèi nǐ zhēng zhàn zhǔ dài nǐ xiàng qián, ràng guò qù suí shí guāng zǒu yuǎn,
 tiān guó jìn le, suí zǒu suí chuán, wàn mín liú guī zhǔ shèng shān.</lyrics>
<title>tā néng bāng nǐ 迦南313</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
